node.text: It’s Money Moves time and we’re continuing the conversation about credit! Remember, it’s never too late to get started. #HartOfItAll #MoneyMoves #ChasePartner @chase

node.text: It’s Money Moves time and today we’re talking about Credit! Everything from defining credit to why it’s important to have good credit. Not only do I talk about my challenges with maintaining good credit over the years, but I also share a few tips that I wish someone would have taught me earlier in life. It’s never too early… or too late to get started. Check out my IG story for some important tips!  #HartOfItAll #MoneyMoves #ChasePartner @chase
